* Lineage\nLimitations
** Not preserved on rename
***_ Renaming a table breaks lineage link
***_ Previous name loses connection
** Path-based access
***_ delta.'abfss://...' shows path only
***_ Not the table name
** Not captured
***_ Global temporary views
***_ system.information_schema tables
***_ Some UDFs obscure column lineage
** Design recommendations
***_ Use 3-level namespace (catalog.schema.table)
***_ Avoid path-based access
***_ Use UC-enabled compute for all production
@endmindmap
